{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Only the first 3 levels are available in the demo.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chaos at the headquarters of the video game organization, UPIXO: the villain, El Pix, has stolen some important and historically valuable artifacts of video game history from the archive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Help Chubby retrieve all the artifacts from El Pix's icy realm of Snowdriftland!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/story.png?t=1734468167\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>GAME CONCEPT</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mission in Snowdriftland is unique in its concept: Play it like a traditional Advent calendar, and select a level every day and let Chubby guide you through the cold winter days. Or play it like a classic platformer - any time you want.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/map.gif?t=1734468167\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SUITABLE FOR ALL</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mission in Snowdriftland offers the right gaming experience for all players: younger and less experienced gamers can get off to a quick and easy start and jump right in to start searching for the artifacts, while core gamers will face a cool challenge as they collect all 24 snowflakes per level.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/eliminate_pinkus.gif?t=1734468167\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/ingame.jpg?t=1734468167\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CRAZY WORLDS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Prepare to confront some wacky enemies like penguins in squirrel costumes, polar bear joggers listening to music, flaming fire bumblebees and many more.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/store_creatures_01.gif?t=1734468167\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/store_creatures_02.gif?t=1734468167\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>SECRET AREAS</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore Secret Areas containing strange Glitch Pixels in every level. Collect them all to solve the secret behind the odd Pixel Mass found in the newly discovered Hole!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/secretareas.jpg?t=1734468167\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>MINIBOSSES (ONLY IN FULL VERSION)</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Compete against four Minibosses, the subordinates of El Pix, who are standing in your way after every world. Defeat them to prove that you can face the big boss himself! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/minibosse.jpg?t=1734468167\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>FEATURES</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Secret areas </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pixel art </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Retro music </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Full controller support </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Speedrun timer  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Achievements</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>DEMO</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Only the first 3 levels are available in the demo</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong> FULL VERSION</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">24 levels + huge bonus level + 1 end boss battle</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 different worlds</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mini boss battles in each world</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Chubby is on another mission...<i>will you join him?</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/extras/pinku_walk.gif?t=1734468167\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1734468167","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/page.bg.jpg?t=1734468167","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/d3496459f46384a86253dbf0aeb687f14ef70661/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1734468167","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1560650/d3496459f46384a86253dbf0aeb687f14ef70661/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1734468167","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achievements","id":22},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28},{"description":"Remote Play on TV","id":43}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>Only the first 3 levels are available in the demo.</strong></i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>STORY</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Chaos at the headquarters of the video game organization, UPIXO: the villain, El Pix, has stolen some important and historically valuable artifacts of video gam